This plugin can be used to estimate nonlinear distortions induced by the image acquisition process<ref>{{cite journal|author=Verena Kaynig, Bernd Fischer, Elisabeth MÃ¼ller, and Joachim M. Buhmann|title=Fully automatic stitching and distortion correction of transmission electron microscope images|journal=Journal of Structural Biology|year=2010|volume=171(2)|page=163-173|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6WM5-50106VP-1&_user=10&_coverDate=08/31/2010&_rdoc=1&_fmt=high&_orig=search&_sort=d&_docanchor=&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=1d165c88d80bf6db0a4d91f9dafa48c7|doi=10.1016/j.jsb.2010.04.012 }}</ref>
